<TEI xmlns:ns0="http://tei-c.org"><text><body><div><p><note n="a" /><orgName key="Melguèlh, homes de o melgoresos" xml:id="org1" role="jurador">Homines Melgorienses</orgName> iuraverunt ad <persName key="Barcelona, comte de" xml:id="pers1" role="beneficiari">comitem Barchinonensem</persName> fidelitatem de corpore suo et de <placeName key="Melguèlh, vila i castell" type="vila i castell" xml:id="loc1">castello et de villa de Melguir</placeName> et de toto <placeName key="Melguèlh, comtat de" type="comtat" xml:id="loc2">honore Melgorii</placeName>. Et fecerunt ei hominium propriis manibus. In primis, iuravit <persName key="Poncius" xml:id="pers2" role="jurador">Poncius</persName>, miles de Obelo. <persName key="Raimon de Bellog" xml:id="pers3" role="jurador">Raimon de <hi rend="italic">Bellog</hi></persName>, miles. <persName key="Oliver" xml:id="pers4" role="jurador"><hi rend="italic">Oliver</hi></persName>, miles. <persName key="Rater" xml:id="pers5" role="jurador"><hi rend="italic">Rater</hi></persName>. <persName key="Bertran Maltos" xml:id="pers6" role="jurador">Bertran <hi rend="italic">Maltos</hi></persName>. <persName key="Raimon Gandalmar" xml:id="pers7" role="jurador"><hi rend="italic">Raimon Gandalmar</hi></persName>. Isti sunt milites.</p> <p><persName key="Ugo de Gavernes" xml:id="pers8" role="jurador">Ugo de <hi rend="italic">Gavernes</hi></persName>. <persName key="Guillem Rostan" xml:id="pers9" role="jurador"><hi rend="italic">Guillem Rostan</hi></persName>. <persName key="Raimon Gido" xml:id="pers10" role="jurador"><hi rend="italic">Raimon Gido</hi></persName>. <persName key="Ugo Rigall" xml:id="pers11" role="jurador">Ugo <hi rend="italic">Rigall</hi></persName>. <persName key="Poncius Echard" xml:id="pers12" role="jurador">Poncius <hi rend="italic">Echard</hi></persName>. <persName key="Bernard de Pina" xml:id="pers13" role="jurador"><hi rend="italic">Bernard de Pina</hi></persName>. <persName key="Pelagez" xml:id="pers14" role="jurador"><hi rend="it